message.body: When are you and tyler coming back to northfield?
Well tye isn't with me actually bc I went to the concert and he didnt want to. Then my parents car broke down. So I don't know about him or me... Waiting for news abt the car
Oh sheesh. What concert?
David bazan and cotton jones at the turf club
Oh. Well ok. if either of you needs or wants to be picked up. I'm free pretty much all day.
Thank you. Im with Travis so I'm going to have to wait for the van around these parts. Tyes got a ride lined up I think but I'll let him know
I think I bent my ear when I slept on it.
Does it hurt?
Kind of. I think it'll go away.
Looks like Tyler brought the new ulm army but forgot his sister.
Yep. But I'm on my way
I'm glad and also a little worried about tyler's circus.
Me too. Ugh. Wait to eat with us?
Ya I can do that. I'm very excited to see you. Scotty is too. Really excited.
If you you're up and want some blueberry oatmeal in the morning let me know and I'll make a double batch. Gnight martha.
When do you start working again?
The 20th. Bah
Bah? When do you move to philadelphia?
I don't wantto go back to work. Philadelphia or new York in October
New york with pat?
Yea. I just want to be out there.
You should be in ny. I wish I could go with. Also wish I would have talked with you while you were here. It's absurd. Ugh
Why can't you come? And is it something I did?
I'm just not sure if I can jump that far yet? Maybe I could. I don't know. It wasnt something you did. I hoped I was going to be better at talking.and i wasnt
Anyway it's not as big of a deal as it seems. I had a good night. It was nice being around you. And I look forward to whenever that happens again.
I had a really good night. I'll be down I think before hell starts in the form of finance
